data.description: Experience the allure of this extraordinary waterfront home situated on Meghanis Arm of Lake Jackson. The property boasts a 2872 sqft main residence featuring 4 beds & 3 baths, complemented by an additional 833 sqft detached guest/pool house w/ 1 bed, 1 bath, kitchen, & open living space. Adding to the charm is an 861 sqft game/theater room w/ a full bath, not included in the advertised square footage. This versatile structure, accessed through a private drive, could serve as an ideal home office or art studio. The main house is designed w/ open living & a thoughtfully laid-out split bedroom floor plan w/ 2 fireplaces. The main bedroom suite stands out w/ its private office/sitting room overlooking the pool, a luxurious bath w/ a jetted tub, private laundry facilities, & a stunning master suite. Nestled on a sprawling 1.28-acre lot, the property backs up to Meghanis Arm of Lake Jackson, providing a kayak launch & easy access to the lake for excellent fishing opportunities. This property is a must-see to truly grasp & appreciate the multitude of features it has to offer.
